quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  84,1,"Si asmaan o fettii."
  84,2,"Mbo he…ótii joom mbo hakke woodani mbo."
  84,3,"Si lesdi foo…ótaama."
  84,4,"Ndi wernii ko woni e hendi ndi acciti."
  84,5,"Mbo he…ótii joom mbo hakke woodani mbo."
  84,6,"Ehey maa ne…ó…óo aan ko a tampoowa golloowo fa'ade e joom ma ko a kawroowo e mum."
  84,7,"Si tawi ko oon tottiraa…óo deftere mum junnga √Īaama mum."
  84,8,"Arma o haasbe haasbeere newiinde."
  84,9,"O rutto to banndiraa…ďe mum ko o beltii…óo."
  84,10,"Si tawi ko oon tottiraa…óo deftere mum caggal ke'eci makko."
  84,11,"Arma ma o noddu halkaare."
  84,12,"O naatnee jayngol."
  84,13,"Pellet o woniina beltii…óe e ndeer koreeji mum."
  84,14,"Pellet o scikkunoo…óa o ruttataaka."
  84,15,"Oho kay pellet joom makko na yi'a mbo."
  84,16,"Mbo…óa woo…óndira mbo…óeeri koode saanga mutal."
  84,17,"O woo…óndiri jehma e kombo mofti."
  84,18,"O woo…óndirii lewru sundu renndii."
  84,19,"Ma on peewnire tigi ommboo…óe e dow ommboo…óe."
  84,20,"Hol ko ha…ói …ďee gooŇč…óin'de."
  84,21,"Si alquraana janngaama e dow mu'en …ďe cujjata."
  84,22,"Woni kay ko …ďeen he'efaree…ďe ko yeddoo…ďe."
  84,23,"Ko Alla …ďuri anndu ko …ďe coomi e …ďer…óe mu'en."
  84,24,"Habru…ďe lepte mu'us…óe."
  84,25,"Si wona …ďeen goŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆ī …óe, hino woodani …ďe njo…ďdi ndi ta∆īondirtaa."
